Tavatron thought for a moment. She too would rather be hunting or practicing 
battle manuvers than sitting indoors doing nothing. Nothing, she'd been 
doing too much of that lately. Spending time with Dinobot had been a 
pleasent change of pace.

"Yes, if you don't mind reading." Tavatron turned and headed down one of the 
ark's many halls.
